<h2>Visa Debit Card</h2>
<p>Leave your checkbook at home. The HSFCU Visa&reg; Check Card lets you carry your checkbook in your wallet, and offers these other advantages: </p>
<ul>
	<li>Quick and simple to use </li>
    <li>Pay for up to $1,000 in purchases at millions of merchants worldwide, wherever Visa debit is accepted </li>
    <li>No waiting for check approval   </li>
    <li>Less need to write checks</li>
    <li>No worry that an &quot;out of town&quot; check won't be honored  </li>
    <li>Can also be used for making purchases online or by phone </li>
    <li>Doubles as an ATM card - use it to get up to $300 in cash per day at more than a million Visa ATMs worldwide or at any ATM in the STAR network</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="bold">The Visa Check Card is free with an HSFCU checking account.</span> To receive a Visa Check Card, contact an HSFCU representative or call 703-776-2700.</p>
<p>As our valued customer, Healthcare Systems FCU offers you Verified by Visa.   Verified by Visa puts you in control when shopping online: only you can approve purchases using your private password. </p>
